title: War of the Roses: He Left His Phone at Target
description: Tina started dating her boyfriend when he cheated on his girlfriend with her so she already doesn't trust him a ton.  Now he's spending hours at Target and Home Depot according to tracking his phone and she doesn't trust he's actually there shopping for that long.
